CHAT.comment: Nina will be two years old on November 19 , 1970. she has started putting words together into sentences during the past two months. from september 5 through october 24 she was separated from her mother and was living with her father in Providence , Rhode island. she arrived in Calififornia to join her mother on October 24. during the first week she was quite upset. she had a lot of trouble sleeping at night and had many temper tantrums. she showed a great fear of being abandoned by her mother. however , during the past few days she seems to be much more secure. she seems to have adjusted well to being left with a baby sitter. hour 1 is recorded in her own room. we are looking at nina's new abc book. nina loves to read books.
